00:16:47.579 --> 00:16:50.299
and I see his response to Eliphaz,

00:16:50.299 --> 00:16:53.899
and I consider his response to Bildad in chapter 19,

00:16:53.899 --> 00:16:56.619
and we see the impact of our words,

00:16:56.619 --> 00:16:59.579
but the stated intent or purpose of Job

00:16:59.579 --> 00:17:01.940
on how he would use his words,

00:17:01.940 --> 00:17:03.419
I then notice this.

00:17:03.419 --> 00:17:04.819
If you're taking notes number three,

00:17:04.819 --> 00:17:07.659
I want you to note the testimony of Job.

00:17:07.659 --> 00:17:11.139
It's interesting that here in chapter number 16,

00:17:11.339 --> 00:17:13.739
Job is answering Eliphaz,

00:17:13.739 --> 00:17:15.299
and as he's answering Eliphaz,

00:17:15.299 --> 00:17:17.259
he says, here's what you guys have done,

